Constructor Detail

BloomFilter

public BloomFilter(int estimatedMembers,
                   byte[] seed)
Deprecated. 
Constructor

Parameters:
estimatedMembers - The performance of the bloom filter can be improved by accurately estimating the number of members that will be inserted into it. Too low a number will increase the likelihood of false positives. Too high a number will cause the filter to be larger than necessary, impacting performance. It is better for this number to be too low than too high.
seed - Random seed data must be of length 4

decode

public void decode(XMLDecoder decoder)
            throws ContentDecodingException
Deprecated. 
Description copied from interface: XMLEncodable
Decode this object during an ongoing decoding pass; this is what subclasses generally need to know how to implement. Reads just the object itself, higher-level processes have handled start and end document if need be. Allows object to be read using the same code whether it is a top-level element written alone, or nested inside another element.
